text: Voices of Spring (German: Frühlingsstimmen) is a 1952 Austrian musical movie directed by Hans Thimig and starring Paul Hörbiger, Hans Jaray, Senta Wengraf, Fritz von Friedl, Susi Nicoletti, Christl Mardayn, Adrienne Gessner. ==Other websites== * Category:1952 musical movies Category:Austrian musical movies
title: Voices of Spring (1952 movie)
